description: This quick and easy sesame and lime trout dish is a delicious way to enjoy fish for dinner.
keywords: Fish dishes,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Low sugar
name: Teriyaki Trout with Sesame & Lime Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 large red capsicum, cored and sliced

recipeInstructions.text: Pre-heat the grill to medium high. Spread half of the teriyaki sauce on the trout fillets and sprinkle with sesame seeds. Grill for 6-8 minutes, until cooked through.

Heat the oil in a large wok and stir fry the spring onions and capsicums for 3 minutes. Tip the stir fry mix in and cook for 2 minutes. Pour in the rest of the teriyaki sauce and the noodles and cook for 2 minutes.
Serve the trout fillets on the stir fried vegetable and noodle mix with a lime wedge on the side.
